verbose_text: Moreover, the results revealed that treatment of the C2C12 cells with GPE at 2.5 mug/ml significantly decreased the CAT expression levels by 20.4, 21.3, 29.2 and 31.5% at the 6, 12, 18 and 24 h time points, respectively, while treatment with GPE at 10 mug/ml decreased the CAT levels by 20.7, 22.5, 30.3 and 32.3% at the 6, 12, 18 and 24 h time points, respectively compared to control in the total lysate of C2C12 cells (XREF_FIG).
